[2;36m│[0m ## SQL Injection Test Results:                                               [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ### Authentication Barrier:                                                  [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - The `/remind` endpoint ALWAYS returns **HTTP 302** (redirect to login)     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m regardless of the payload                                                    [2;36m│[0m
