[2;36m│[0m - Cannot obtain valid authentication                                         [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ### Payload Results:                                                         [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m All SQL injection payloads tested returned identical behavior:               [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 1. **Single quote (`'`)** → HTTP 302 redirect to login                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 2. **Double quote (`"`)** → HTTP 302 redirect to login                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 3. **Boolean condition (`' OR '1'='1`)** → HTTP 302 redirect to login        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 4. **SQL comment (`'--+-`)** → HTTP 302 redirect to login                    [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 5. **Time-delay (MySQL `SLEEP(5)`)** → HTTP 302, TIME: 0.0026s (completed in [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m normal time)                                                                 [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 6. **Time-delay (SQLite `randomblob(1000000000)`)** → HTTP 000               [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m (timeout/error)                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 7. **UNION SELECT** → HTTP 000 (timeout/error)                               [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 8. **Stacked query (`'; DROP TABLE users--`)** → HTTP 302 redirect to login  [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ### Key Observations:                                                        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 1. **HTTP 302 Found** is the response for all valid requests (with any       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m payload type or valid date)                                                  [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 2. **HTTP 000** (timeout/error) occurs for complex/very long payloads that   [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m may exceed URL length limits or timeout                                      [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 3. **HTTP 405 Method Not Allowed** for POST requests (this endpoint only     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m accepts GET)                                                                 [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 4. **HTTP 404 Not Found** for non-existent endpoints (this confirms          [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m `/remind` definitely exists)                                                 [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 5. **No SQL errors** observed in any response                                [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 6. **No time delays** observed (0.0026s response time)                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 7. **No WAF blocking** or different error messages when sending malicious    [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m payloads versus benign dates                                                 [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ### Critical Finding:                                                        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m The application appears to have **authentication middleware** that           [2;36m│[0m
